PROJECT: Game Wiki Page

Project Description: The game dark souls can be very difficult and usually does not have a lot of guidance for the playyers. There are a lot of items, places, NPCs, quests, ect. Making sense of all of them can be very difficult at times. Sometimes the players need some guidance for things like how to use an item, where to go next, or how to interact with a character. Creating a wiki can allow players to find and share helpful informationfor the game

Project Requirements:
Pages:
  Homepage
  About Page
  NPC Page
  Item Page
  Weapon Page 
  Armour Page
  Enemy Page
  Chat Pages
Features:
  Ability for users to generate pages
  Ability to search pages
  Chat Rooms 
  Ability to comment on pages
  Gear analytics/build creator
  Ability to rate items
